{"tid":2091900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三年前被捕捱打 吳文遠控兩警索償","createTime":"2020-07-03T02:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T03:03:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7432d534d489194a8f141357901a6a64a0b89ce","tid":2091900,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:44:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/WUQRLPAJGG4SE2OYT4EQCSKO5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FWUQRLPAJGG4SE2OYT4EQCSKO5E%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBL32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=f7d714da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FWUQRLPAJGG4SE2OYT4EQCSKO5E%2F&h=4581bd5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/WUQRLPAJGG4SE2OYT4EQCSKO5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n三年前被捕捱打 吳文遠控兩警索償<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EOFakDLxYwfGsyAo-GFgOfz-3ZU=/652x468/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q2VIDOBB2TJC3S3OKGZWNKHTBI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEOFakDLxYwfGsyAo-GFgOfz-3ZU%3D%2F652x468%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ2VIDOBB2TJC3S3OKGZWNKHTBI.gif&h=5a68e67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當日吳文遠被警員拘捕後，雙手雙腳朝天被帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社民連與香港眾志於2017年七．一當日到金紫荊廣場抗議，甫抵達即遭過百名藍絲包圍毆打。警方其後卻拘捕吳文遠及長毛等人，吳文遠更稱在警車上遭警員以粗口辱罵、扯頭髮及踢下體，日前入稟區域法院指警方侵害人身，要求政府及涉案兩名警長賠償。<br />\n<br />\n原告吳文遠控告律政司司長、警長2295及警長15163。入稟狀指，兩名警長於2017年7月1日在灣仔軒尼詩道138號對原告施加侵權及不合法的武力，政府須為相關行為負責。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n監警會至今未有結果<br />\n<br />\n原告要求法庭宣佈<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n相關利息與訟費。<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠曾召開記者會，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n並兩度踢吳的下體。<br />\n<br />\n當時吳大喊救命，但車外無人聽到。另一警員則扯住吳的頭髮，將吳的頭撞向警車車窗。<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠曾經向投訴警察課舉報，監警會事隔兩年才收到並且審核調查報告，惟至今未有結果。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCPI2035/20"},{"pid":"01958eb74c080a97fa79cef834c623a1ff6c767e","tid":2091900,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:59:30.000Z","msg":"三萬幾蚊一個月都唔識控制情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c78c79874f1419a7f0e30f37ed8b6fa9e2d87c","tid":2091900,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"三年前仲可以搵到警長編號告鳩佢"},{"pid":"eafbb40dce4d8b847f9414ef68f285d2299408b3","tid":2091900,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7432d534d489194a8f141357901a6a64a0b89ce","tid":2091900,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:44:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/WUQRLPAJGG4SE2OYT4EQCSKO5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FWUQRLPAJGG4SE2OYT4EQCSKO5E%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBL32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=f7d714da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FWUQRLPAJGG4SE2OYT4EQCSKO5E%2F&h=4581bd5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/WUQRLPAJGG4SE2OYT4EQCSKO5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n三年前被捕捱打 吳文遠控兩警索償<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EOFakDLxYwfGsyAo-GFgOfz-3ZU=/652x468/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q2VIDOBB2TJC3S3OKGZWNKHTBI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEOFakDLxYwfGsyAo-GFgOfz-3ZU%3D%2F652x468%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ2VIDOBB2TJC3S3OKGZWNKHTBI.gif&h=5a68e67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當日吳文遠被警員拘捕後，雙手雙腳朝天被帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社民連與香港眾志於2017年七．一當日到金紫荊廣場抗議，甫抵達即遭過百名藍絲包圍毆打。警方其後卻拘捕吳文遠及長毛等人，吳文遠更稱在警車上遭警員以粗口辱罵、扯頭髮及踢下體，日前入稟區域法院指警方侵害人身，要求政府及涉案兩名警長賠償。<br />\n<br />\n原告吳文遠控告律政司司長